.

7. Frontend (UI)

Built with HTML + CSS + JavaScript.

Browser has a built-in HTML interpreter to convert markup â†’ UI.

HTML Basics

Tags are predefined.

Structure:

<html>
  <head>
    <title>Page Title</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- Content -->
  </body>
</html>


Common Tags: <h1>â€¦<h6>, <b>, <i>, <u>, <br>, <p>, <div>, <span>, <ul>, <ol>, <li>, <table>, <img>, <audio>, <video>, <input>.

Attributes = key-value pairs in opening tag (e.g., <table border="1">).

Empty tags = No closing tag (<br/>, <img>).

